text: @Cedric_Benson , Rebel Dad #33, Great job Ced, keep your head up shoulders square and 1st step!
Dear Lord, give me the strength to carry out Your will and to stay positive throughout this difficult day.
Big Ang is a crazy show.
Dear Lord, I give you my hands to do Your work; I give You my feet to go Your way; I give You my eyes to see as You see.
My God, I believe in You and all that You have taught, because You have said it, and Your word is true.
Dear Lord, I choose to follow You in all my ways.
